{"tid":1597583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔x掂喎　C朗近24次罰球全炒","createTime":"2019-09-27T04:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T04:20:21.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e5dddb22e96fe96f37cf697fd2634f598f4807","tid":1597583,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">62.5% 唔中龍</span><br />\n<br />\n 意大利傳媒發表意甲數據，其中有一項關於C朗射罰球，結果發現，呢位葡萄牙球王最近24次主射罰球當中，1球都未入過，反而佢嘅祖記隊友比真歷，射6次入1球。<br />\n<br />\n呢項數據係由《Ultimo Uomo》發表，截至前仗對維羅納為止，C朗為祖雲達斯在意甲及歐聯主射24次罰球，<span style=\"color: red;\">結果15球中人牆、2次射斜、7次被門將撲出，入球率係0呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n反而比真歷喺對拿玻里嘅大戰，射入1個罰球。而佢喺2015至18年期間，就入咗11個罰球。"},{"pid":"d262d089a7a6f6a309db416ff1abc4a8792f0126","tid":1597583,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">數據出錯! 70.8% 唔中龍</span>"},{"pid":"05e3aa5fbd2c6e70703d652213763453a72caca3","tid":1597583,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=ed652c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n公海：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lennonway_public\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flennonway_public&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=d4160c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lennonway_public</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpDxbbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpDxbbY.jpg&h=859cc815&s={SIZE}\" /><im